review:
Best 2020 survival simulator:
1) keep your nose and mouth covered;
2) courier is the most valuable job;
3) increase social distancing with baby blob in front and Odradek behind;
4) take long lone walk - run away from the crowded places;
5) dont forget to wash yourself after every walk;
6) avoid transport as much as possible.

